OL,3,CPods to be installed for rough
OL,4,Csleepers in seaside town
OL,6,FA council has approved plans to
OL,7,Finstall four "emergency accommodation
OL,8,Fpods" for homeless people in Skegness.
OL,10,FThe units, created by Amazing Grace
OL,11,FSpaces, are designed for people who
OL,12,Fhave been sleeping on the streets and
OL,13,Fwho cannot be housed in hostels due to
OL,14,Fcomplex needs.
OL,16,FThey include a toilet, wash basin and
OL,17,Fa bed and have a coded lock on the
OL,18,Fdoor and will cost the council
OL,19,F#70,000, with #10,000 allocated as a
OL,20,Fcontingency fund.
