OL,3,CPods to be installed for rough
OL,4,Csleepers in seaside town
OL,6,FEast Lindsey District Council said it
OL,7,Fwas a "vital step" in supporting
OL,8,FSkegness's homeless community.
OL,10,FCllr Sarah Devereux said: "The
OL,11,Fintroduction of these accommodation
OL,12,Fpods is a vital step in our mission to
OL,13,Fsupport our homeless community.
OL,15,F"These pods provide immediate shelter,
OL,16,Fwarmth, and safety, while we work with
OL,17,Findividuals to find more permanent
OL,18,Fsolutions. We are committed to
OL,19,Fensuring that everyone has access to
OL,20,Fsafe and dignified living conditions."
