OL,3,CPods to be installed for rough
OL,4,Csleepers in seaside town
OL,6,FThere were 167 people sleeping rough
OL,7,Fin the East Lindsey district in 2023-
OL,8,F24. Nearly three quarters were located
OL,9,Fin Skegness.
OL,11,FCllr William Gray, the portfolio
OL,12,Fholder for communities, said: "This
OL,13,Fapproval is a testament to our
OL,14,Fcommitment to improving housing
OL,15,Foptions for our community.
OL,17,F"These pods will offer safe and secure
OL,18,Faccommodation for individuals who are
OL,19,Ffacing housing challenges."
